    <item>
      <title>特朗普特别检察官报告发布遭法院搁置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/special-counsel-release-of-trump-report-left-in-limbo-by-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院不会阻止司法部长梅里克·加兰德 (Merrick Garland) 发布特别顾问的报告，该报告详细说明了他对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的刑事调查结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/special-counsel-release-of-trump-report-left-in-limbo-by-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 01:07:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯取消海外之行，专注于山火应对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/harris-cancels-overseas-trip-to-focus-on-wildfire-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯取消了三国出访，留在美国协助联邦政府应对其家乡加利福尼亚州的灾难性山火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/harris-cancels-overseas-trip-to-focus-on-wildfire-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 00:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院允许特朗普就纽约封口费案进行量刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/supreme-court-allows-trump-s-sentencing-in-ny-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院因意见分歧为候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的封口费刑事案件宣判扫清了道路，这对准备开始第二任期的他来说是一个挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/supreme-court-allows-trump-s-sentencing-in-ny-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 00:15:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普警告委内瑞拉不要伤害反对派领导人马查多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/trump-warns-venezuela-not-to-harm-opposition-leader-machado</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普首次公开评论委内瑞拉有争议的选举，他敦促委内瑞拉不要伤害反对派领导人玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多（María Corina Machado）。周四，马查多遭到短暂逮捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/trump-warns-venezuela-not-to-harm-opposition-leader-machado</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 23:20:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南共产党加入马斯克和米莱的行列，削减政府开支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/vietnam-s-communists-join-musk-milei-in-slashing-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在埃隆·马斯克和阿根廷的哈维尔·米莱倡导大幅削减政府规模的雄心勃勃的计划的同时，全球各地具有完全不同意识形态的政治领导人也在开展类似的努力：越南共产党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/vietnam-s-communists-join-musk-milei-in-slashing-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国市场动荡一周后，里夫斯力争深化与中国的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/reeves-bids-to-deepen-china-ties-after-week-of-uk-market-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周末，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯将成为七年来访问北京的最高级英国官员，在英国市场动荡有可能破坏其刺激国内增长计划的背景下，她将着手深化与中国的经济联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/reeves-bids-to-deepen-china-ties-after-week-of-uk-market-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登增加联邦援助以应对“灾难性”火灾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/biden-surges-aid-to-california-to-address-catastrophic-fires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他正在增加对加州的联邦援助，因为加州正在应对肆虐社区的野火，并已敦促加州州长加文·纽瑟姆不惜一切代价扑灭致命的大火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/biden-surges-aid-to-california-to-address-catastrophic-fires</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 22:07:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗针对反对派 委内瑞拉两小时逮捕行动震惊世界</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/maduro-s-nemesis-joins-protests-denouncing-his-win-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多于周四被委内瑞拉尼古拉斯·马杜罗政权逮捕之前，她再次出现在公众面前，强烈地提醒人们她去年夏天领导的反对派运动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/maduro-s-nemesis-joins-protests-denouncing-his-win-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:39:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果特朗普征收关税，加拿大将对美国橙汁和钢铁征收反击税：美联社</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-09/florida-orange-juice-and-steel-will-be-on-canada-s-list-for-retaliation-if-trump-imposes-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多（美联社）——一位知情的高级官员周四表示，如果美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现对所有加拿大产品征收 25% 关税的威胁，加拿大正考虑对美国橙汁、马桶和一些钢铁产品征收报复性关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-09/florida-orange-juice-and-steel-will-be-on-canada-s-list-for-retaliation-if-trump-imposes-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 17:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
